com.clarionmedia.infinitum.di
Interface BeanFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
ConfigurableBeanFactory
public interface BeanFactory

Stores beans that have been configured in infinitum.cfg.xml. The BeanProvider acts as a service locator for InfinitumContext. Beans are retrieved by their name and registered by providing a name, class, and field values.

BeanFactory is responsible for maintaining a bean registry, initializing bean instances, and performing any necessary dependency injections.
